{"tid":2508954,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「是日超高質黃店系列」點心小店 蒸盧@黃埔","createTime":"2021-04-29T06:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T06:45:43.000Z","uid":22108,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d5aa02383ed620dfcaff8f56178cb7c39db025","tid":2508954,"uid":22108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"放Lunch唔就腳都要特登行過黎<br />\n叫左雲石流心芝麻包，燒賣，珍珠雞<br />\n一個人食飽到仆街<br />\n<br />\n芝麻包誠意之作<br />\n雲石包皮打卡一流 咬開仲有啖啖流心芝麻餡<br />\n燒賣大大粒真材實料 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZb93BRLEZN8RPV1bZ2eNcsBuZCivPndhsv73BEV99h2V?filename=qTyMy7j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTyMy7j.png&h=3368e3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珍珠雞就不過不失冇咩特別<br />\n有d淡同乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU1v8rabrBVTaf3cjHFxxJtKVzPrYsaMnH2Bjh1kp8VSx?filename=Rfydebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfydebc.png&h=028129e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇收茶錢冇加一<br />\n埋單86 算抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f4a3ede8508fde3d690ed67f01d6dd92ad7d4d","tid":2508954,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:36:07.000Z","msg":"一個人食3籠野你都幾食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9691489b4a707c82afc0c52e1c470f8d5f8d57d0","tid":2508954,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7aeecf85fac835f19809a72d286921d749b1462","tid":2508954,"uid":362865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"燒賣要擺粒乒乓波喺到先明白有幾震撼"},{"pid":"09a4b45b1fe1beba206c6ce9c152eda773566d41","tid":2508954,"uid":22108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f4a3ede8508fde3d690ed67f01d6dd92ad7d4d","tid":2508954,"